title: T206 Russ Ford error double strike Tolstoi wet sheet transfer

posts.post_title: T206 Russ Ford error double strike Tolstoi wet sheet transfer
posts.post_content: What you see is what you get, rough condition but very rare.  Looking for 1000 but willing to listen to reasonable offers.  The red wet transfer is from the T68 set Heroes of History and features Irish Patriot Robert Emmett
